text: The women's 'Individual Aero Kickboxing without Step' category involved eleven women from six countries across two continents (Europe and North America). Each contestant went through five performances (1.5 to 2 minutes each) with the totals added up at the end of the event. The gold medal winner was Slovenian Bianca Barada-Tapilatu, Hungary's Brigitta Gazdag claimed silver, and Italy's Laura Fiori got another bronze medal (she also won a bronze in the other individual Aero Kickboxing category). ==Results== {| class="wikitable" |- !
